      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just don't know how many more mornings i can do this. the nerve pain is so constant it feels like i'm being electrocuted while i'm just trying to sleep. i'm so tired of fighting for a life that just feels like a punishment. sometimes it feels like the only real mercy would be if everything just... stopped.",
